      "cookedHtml": "<p><strong>Hello everyone,</strong></p>\n<p>As a developer, I’m currently using <a href=\"https://Make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">make.com</a> to set up <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> accounts for people because <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>’s automations are still quite limited. However, I’ve noticed that <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>’s workflows are starting to resemble <a href=\"https://make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">make.com</a>/<a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">zapier</a>, for example, in the a later step of an workflow you can map the information from the first steps. This is amazing, and I hope that very soon we will be able to integrate with external apps like <a href=\"https://quickbooks.intuit.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">QB</a>, <a href=\"https://mailchimp.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">mailchimp</a>, etc… using <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> workflows as well.</p>\n<p>I would like to request that <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> should re-allow workflows for all plans and not only for enterprise. Many companies may not need the enterprise plan, but they still require the functionality of workflows. As developers, we have our <a href=\"http://make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">make.com</a> accounts that cost us money, and it gets very messy. If we had the option to build everything that we need within <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, it would be amazing.</p>\n<p><strong>Dear <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, please allow us partners to use workflows in all plans.</strong></p>\n<p>I would like to give you some examples of how I use <a href=\"http://make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">make.com</a>, and if this were an option to do it directly within <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, I would be more than happy.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/f/4fd53a9c71bdd59fd0c434935a86175df518e42e.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134529\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/f/4fd53a9c71bdd59fd0c434935a86175df518e42e_2_517x333.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134529\" width=\"517\" height=\"333\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-09-22 134529</span><span class=\"informations\">1204×777 63.5 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/0/3022d28f282f02624190b55a247a8142c33731d1.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134601\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/0/3022d28f282f02624190b55a247a8142c33731d1_2_517x301.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134601\" width=\"517\" height=\"301\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-09-22 134601</span><span class=\"informations\">1315×768 78 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/0/301a94bedb36224f5a2d23dbe6e864b7a4bc08ff.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134640\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/0/301a94bedb36224f5a2d23dbe6e864b7a4bc08ff_2_517x342.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134640\" width=\"517\" height=\"342\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-09-22 134640</span><span class=\"informations\">1387×919 68 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/b/cbe04b695778f559b53f2283a9884e6f9c8571cb.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134656\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/b/cbe04b695778f559b53f2283a9884e6f9c8571cb_2_517x318.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 134656\" width=\"517\" height=\"318\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-09-22 134656</span><span class=\"informations\">1482×912 81.8 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/8/781c61dbe6dc1ee9c5dd6cfdc34e7d9226d94823.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 163359\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/8/781c61dbe6dc1ee9c5dd6cfdc34e7d9226d94823_2_517x262.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 163359\" width=\"517\" height=\"262\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-09-22 163359</span><span class=\"informations\">1551×787 35.6 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/a/1aa234dd6a7d549659324bc599dd5103eee080cb.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 163308\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/a/1aa234dd6a7d549659324bc599dd5103eee080cb_2_517x288.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 163308\" width=\"517\" height=\"288\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-09-22 163308</span><span class=\"informations\">1366×761 45.3 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/7/e7b43c1dd02c1fbcade4e52f146072d2ce1cbe05.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-09-22 163239\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/7/e7b43c1dd0